By and large the spellblades hail from the ranks of spellcasters, be they mages, psionicists or sorcerers. While their magical talents may differ, they all share a desire to meld their magic with steel. Being originally primarily
spellcasters who shun melee combat, the first step in their goal was to bolster their presence in melee. To this end a rigorous training regime was devised, which sought to capitalize on the spellcaster's sharp mind and magic, augmenting his skills in all aspects of melee.
