Each of the founding guilds that created the Golden Company have their own
view on how the astral order should best be kept. The guilds are not in
competition, but seek to complement one another to create the perfect
specimen.

The guild of the Paladins uses their religious fervor to fuel the defensive
capabilities of the Golden Arts.

The guild of the Healers use their restorative energies to heal and to
preserve all living things so that no spark of life should ever go to waste.

The guild of the Druids provide the Golden Company with mastery over the
elements, most importantly that of the fire found within the stars.

The guild of the Rangers possesses invaluable information about the
coexistence between all manner of living creatures.

Each of the individual guilds brings together their expertise to fuel
the Golden Arts in different ways, known only to the invokers of the
Golden Company.
