Skill type:        special
Affecting stat(s): skill percent

The Golden Company consists mostly of scholarly types, ponderous and 
full of wisdom. Their interests lie not on the tactical scale of 
battles, but on the grand scheme of warfare. Any actions they take 
works towards a greater goal; individual battles may go one way or 
another, but the end result is what is important. That is not to say, 
however, that an individual battle should be lost. Through countless 
hours of training the invokers of the Golden Company have found a way 
to strike with deadly ferocity when such a need arises. Fueled by 
their indomitable will, the invokers can, when pushed, best even the 
mightiest of warriors in single combat, using their wisdom and 
knowledge to strike upon a weakness possibly even unknown to the 
adversary themself.
